Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…穹？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.26,0:00:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.93,0:00:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了這樣很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  你手法真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起
